            </div>

            <div style="font-weight:bold; margin-bottom: 10px;">Door County Shipwrecks Guides</div>

            <p>
                Set of 4, 9.5" x 6.5" plastic slates
            </p>
            <p>
                This set of dive guides includes: Bullhead Point, Carrington, Christina Nilsson and the Meridian.
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="http://aqua.wisc.edu/publications/ProductDetails.aspx?productID=432">Order Online</a>
            </p>
        </div>

